reviewText: Ohhhh mannnn! Popping in this inexpensive DVD is basically like being in both a fitness class and a one-on-one training session at the same time. What a workout! I WASN'T READY FOR THIS! #NoPainNoGain

It doesn't take long to feel the burn! Round 5 where you follow Willy Wise doing the speed combinations is a beast! If I master that, I think I could really go take a shot in the ring! W3P - Willy Wise Workout: 3 Degrees of Power
